{
    "meta": {
        "locale": "en",
        "template": "index.mjml",
        "title": "russian translation for index template"
    },
    "body": {
        "logo": {
            "state": {
                "select": "/assets/logo-small.png"
            },
            "attributes": {
                "select": {
                    "name": "Logo url",
                    "options": [
                        "/assets/logo-small.png",
                        "/assets/logo-test.png"
                    ]
                }
            }
        },
        "hello": {
            "state": {
                "text": "Hi welcome to this demo of dynamically generated email template preview! </br> Lets explore some features that was implemented so far.</br> <ul><li>#1 Dynamic content via select element (try to change logo url)</li><li>#2 Dynamic text (you are currenlt reading it!)</li><li>#3 Toggles and checkboxes (try to toggle test button)</li><li>#4 <span class=\"bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-violet-500\">Dynamic<span> styling for elements</li><li>#5 Dynamic content for different locales via JSON schemas</li></ul> </br> And that's about it for now. Thanks! !"
            },
            "attributes": {
                "text": {
                    "name": "Greetings"
                }
            }
        },
        "testButton": {
            "state": {
                "text": "this is test button ",
                "toggle": "true"
            },
            "attributes": {
                "text": {
                    "name": "Test button"
                },
                "toggle": {
                    "name": "Test button visibility",
                    "active": true
                }
            }
        }
    }
}